---
const rawBase = import.meta.env.BASE_URL;
const base = rawBase.endsWith('/') ? rawBase : `${rawBase}/`;
const heroImg = `${base}images/hero.svg`;
---
<section class="relative overflow-hidden">
  <div class="container-page pt-14 md:pt-20 pb-section">
    <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-12 gap-10 lg:gap-14 items-center">
      <div class="lg:col-span-6 reveal">
        <span class="eyebrow">Kamiyama Marugoto College of Technology</span>
        <h1 class="mt-5 text-display-xl font-semibold text-ink">
          テクノロジー×デザインで、<br class="hidden md:block" />
          人間の未来を変える学校。
        </h1>
        <p class="en mt-4">
          A 5-year private college in Kamiyama, Tokushima — nurturing creators who reshape the future with technology, design, and entrepreneurship.
        </p>
        <p class="mt-8 max-w-prose text-ink-soft leading-relaxed">
          神山まるごと高専は、徳島県・神山町に2023年に開校した私立の高等専門学校です。起業家精神とものづくりの力を併せ持つ人を育てます。
          <span class="en mt-2">
            Founded in 2023 in the mountain town of Kamiyama, we combine engineering, design, and entrepreneurship into a single 5-year program.
          </span>
        </p>
        <div class="mt-10 flex flex-wrap gap-3">
          <a class="btn-primary no-underline" href="#about">
            学校を知る
            <span class="text-paper/70 text-xs ml-1">Explore</span>
          </a>
          <a class="btn-outline no-underline" href="#access">
            アクセス
            <span class="text-ink-muted text-xs ml-1">Access</span>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="lg:col-span-6 reveal">
        <figure class="relative aspect-[4/5] md:aspect-[5/6] overflow-hidden rounded-3xl bg-paper-warm ring-1 ring-black/5 shadow-soft">
          <img
            src={heroImg}
            alt="神山町の山あいに佇むキャンパスのイメージ"
            class="h-full w-full object-cover"
            loading="eager"
            decoding="async"
          />
          <figcaption class="absolute bottom-4 left-4 right-4 text-xs text-ink-muted bg-paper/80 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-full px-4 py-2 w-fit">
            Placeholder image — 正式な写真素材に差し替え予定
          </figcaption>
        </figure>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
